lead_paragraph: Lewis Hamilton was booed on the podium after a last-lap collision with Mercedes team mate Nico Rosberg handed the triple Formula One world champion a dramatic first Austrian Grand Prix victory on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Triumphant Hamilton Booed After Rosberg Collision
